statements.sql: select `p`.`ID_Phim`, `p`.`TenPhim`, MONTH(hd.created_at) as thang, SUM(vxp.GiaVe) as tong_doanh_thu, COUNT(vxp.ID_Ve) as so_ve_ban from `hoa_don` as `hd` inner join `ve_xem_phim` as `vxp` on `hd`.`ID_HoaDon` = `vxp`.`ID_HoaDon` inner join `suat_chieu` as `sc` on `vxp`.`ID_SuatChieu` = `sc`.`ID_SuatChieu` inner join `phim` as `p` on `sc`.`ID_Phim` = `p`.`ID_Phim` where `hd`.`TrangThaiXacNhanThanhToan` = 1 and year(`hd`.`created_at`) = '2026' group by `p`.`ID_Phim`, `p`.`TenPhim`, MONTH(hd.created_at) order by `p`.`TenPhim` asc, `thang` asc

select `sc`.`ID_SuatChieu`, `p`.`TenPhim`, `sc`.`GioChieu`, `sc`.`NgayChieu`, `pc`.`TenPhongChieu`, `r`.`TenRap`, MONTH(hd.created_at) as thang, COUNT(vxp.ID_Ve) as so_ve_ban, SUM(vxp.GiaVe) as doanh_thu_suat from `hoa_don` as `hd` inner join `ve_xem_phim` as `vxp` on `hd`.`ID_HoaDon` = `vxp`.`ID_HoaDon` inner join `suat_chieu` as `sc` on `vxp`.`ID_SuatChieu` = `sc`.`ID_SuatChieu` inner join `phim` as `p` on `sc`.`ID_Phim` = `p`.`ID_Phim` inner join `phong_chieu` as `pc` on `sc`.`ID_PhongChieu` = `pc`.`ID_PhongChieu` inner join `rap` as `r` on `sc`.`ID_Rap` = `r`.`ID_Rap` where `hd`.`TrangThaiXacNhanThanhToan` = 1 and year(`hd`.`created_at`) = '2026' group by `sc`.`ID_SuatChieu`, `p`.`TenPhim`, `sc`.`GioChieu`, `sc`.`NgayChieu`, `pc`.`TenPhongChieu`, `r`.`TenRap`, MONTH(hd.created_at) order by `p`.`TenPhim` asc, `thang` asc, `sc`.`NgayChieu` asc, `sc`.`GioChieu` asc
